<section id="gus">
  <div class="container-fluid">
    <div class="row centered">  
      <div class="col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-12">
        <%= link_to ("Gustave"), "#gustave", class: "popup-with-zoom-anim"%>
          <div id="gustave" class="zoom-anim-dialog mfp-hide small-dialog">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-12">
              <h3>Gustave</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-6 col-xs-12">
              <pre>
Las mujeres son venados que te asisten.
Ve las camelias tristes y alborotadas
en las tierras negras de tu sien.
La amargura,
locura en casa, viva y coleando.
Esperar es una virtud en condena
y mis labios observan cual verdugo,
los tuyos un madero de alheña.
              </pre>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-6 col-xs-12">
              <pre>
Los hombres son querubines que te asisten
y la sangre hierve en tu cama.
El azufre brilla en la cuenca de tu pecho.
La tenacidad,
la veracidad,
la fuerza está en el arrebato. 
Recibir es orgullo de Magdalenas
y la cruz en mis piernas
se pinta de tu silueta y tu cautela.
              </pre>
            </div>
          </div>  
      </div>  
    </div> <!-- /row --> 
  </div> <!-- /container -->
</section> <!-- /gustave -->

<section id="the">
  <div class="container-fluid">
    <div class="row centered">  
      <div class="col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-12">
        <%= link_to ("Theseus' Bay"), "#theseus", class: "popup-with-zoom-anim"%>
          <div id="theseus" class="zoom-anim-dialog mfp-hide small-dialog">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-12">
              <h3>Theseus' Bay</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-6 col-xs-12">
              <pre>
What means to wake up alone to me?
How does it feel to wake up alone to me?

Tell me I'm good while I'm waiting
for your ship to arrive to the shore, I'm waiting.
Pray I command all the winds in your favor
and guide all your stars safe to me.

But we promised ourselves not to be tangled by love,
always to believe in the bright of greater goals.
              </pre>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-6 col-xs-12">
              <pre>
I rose every morning to sing among willows
So the sea could be tinted with tears and blue petals.
Extend your flawed sight to the beacon of heaven
that hides within me, afraid to give in. 

Do we promise ourselves to allow this vain despair?
Have you always believed in the bright of greater goals?

I was still trying to stay here for you,
I keep on lying that my tears are shed for you,
that all this fighting was worth for a feigned return.
But now through this roaring bay
I declare my deafeat in perpetual grace.

A life after you.
              </pre>
            </div>
          </div>  
      </div>  
    </div> <!-- /row --> 
  </div> <!-- /container -->
</section> <!-- /theseus -->

<section id="bur">
  <div class="container-fluid">
    <div class="row centered">  
      <div class="col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-12">
        <%= link_to ("A Bursting Thing"), "#bursting", class: "popup-with-zoom-anim"%>
          <div id="bursting" class="zoom-anim-dialog mfp-hide small-dialog">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-12">
              <h3>A Bursting Thing</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-6 col-xs-12">
              <pre>
Who said I was not alive?
Who claimed it was for a while?
I went on crawling like I was about to die,
who kept saying that everything was allright?

True love fits in one hand.
I sought the feeling and saw where it laid,
the strangest fire.
And my heart was breaking, 
my heart was all I had.
That bursting thing is truly not what I am.
              </pre>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-6 col-xs-12">
              <pre>
Things get complicated when you walk the road alone.
Things feel complicated when people say you are torn.

Bring the night so he's gone.
Free my arms so I can fight.
Give me my will so I can rise.
But keep my name, so he can realize.
              </pre>
            </div>
          </div>  
      </div>  
    </div> <!-- /row --> 
  </div> <!-- /container -->
</section> <!-- /bursting -->

